---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="wisdom archive"
  description="hidden archive of symbols, psyche, myth, death, dream, and self-realisation"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-kicker">home / archive index</div>
    <h1>wisdom archive</h1>
    <p>
      a growing hidden archive of writings on
      <a href="/foundations" class="link-blue">foundations</a>,
      <a href="/symbols" class="link-red">symbols</a>,
      <a href="/archetypes" class="link-green">archetypes</a>,
      <a href="/dreams" class="link-blue">dreams</a>,
      <a href="/death" class="link-red">death</a>,
      <a href="/alchemy" class="link-green">alchemy</a>,
      <a href="/mysticism" class="link-blue">mysticism</a>,
      and <a href="/self" class="link-red">self</a>.
    </p>
    <p class="muted">
      built to feel like an old private knowledge site discovered late at night.
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="box">
    <div class="box-title">recommended starting points</div>
    <div class="box-body">
      <div class="grid-links">
        <a href="/foundations">
          <span class="link-title">foundations</span>
          <span class="link-desc">self, ego, persona, shadow, consciousness, and inner development.</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/symbols">
          <span class="link-title">symbols</span>
          <span class="link-desc">fire, fool, serpent, tree of life, mandala, labyrinth, and mirror.</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/archetypes">
          <span class="link-title">archetypes</span>
          <span class="link-desc">hero, shadow, anima, animus, child, trickster, and wise old man.</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/dreams">
          <span class="link-title">dreams</span>
          <span class="link-desc">active imagination, dream symbols, inner dialogue, nightmares, and projection.</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/alchemy">
          <span class="link-title">alchemy</span>
          <span class="link-desc">nigredo, albedo, rubedo, transformation, and the philosopher's stone.</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/death">
          <span class="link-title">death</span>
          <span class="link-desc">dance of death, impermanence, afterlife, memento mori, and rebirth.</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/mysticism">
          <span class="link-title">mysticism</span>
          <span class="link-desc">synchronicity, vision, revelation, the unknown, and hidden meaning.</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/self">
          <span class="link-title">self</span>
          <span class="link-desc">identity, intuition, play, paradox, and the wandering path.</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="box">
    <div class="box-title">main archive wings</div>
    <div class="box-body">
      <p><a href="/foundations" class="link-blue">foundations</a> — self, ego, shadow, consciousness, individuation</p>
      <p><a href="/symbols" class="link-red">symbols</a> — fire, fool, serpent, tree of life, mandala, labyrinth, mirror</p>
      <p><a href="/archetypes" class="link-green">archetypes</a> — hero, shadow, anima, animus, child, trickster, wise old man</p>
      <p><a href="/dreams" class="link-blue">dreams + inner work</a> — active imagination, dream symbols, inner dialogue, nightmares, projection</p>
      <p><a href="/alchemy" class="link-red">alchemy</a> — nigredo, albedo, rubedo, transformation, philosopher's stone</p>
      <p><a href="/mysticism" class="link-green">mysticism</a> — synchronicity, vision, revelation, the unknown, hidden meaning</p>
      <p><a href="/death" class="link-blue">death</a> — dance of death, impermanence, afterlife, memento mori, rebirth</p>
      <p><a href="/self" class="link-red">self</a> — identity, intuition, play, paradox, wanderer</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="box">
    <div class="box-title">archive note</div>
    <div class="box-body">
      <p class="muted">
        this is meant to grow into a large timeless text vault rather than a polished modern brand site.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>